  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study has been designed to investigate the comparative effects of sitagliptin vs.
      pioglitazone as add-on treatments in patients with type 2 diabetes who were uncontrolled on
      the full-dose of metformin and sulfonylurea
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
